 First we followed the same g.s. calculation as JENDL to try to   9344 1451
 reproduce all the g.s. cross sections. Then the same parameters  9344 1451
 are employed to calculate cross sections on the excited state,   9344 1451
 with the coupling of 1+, 2+, 3+, and 4+ states.                  9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
 MF1 MT452, 455, 456                                              9344 1451
    same as ground state                                          9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
 MF2                                                              9344 1451
    the same resonance parameters for the ground state,           9344 1451
