                                                                  9344 1451
 MF3                                                              9344 1451
    The following cross sections were evaluated by applying       9344 1451
    a scaling factor of F to the ground state cross sections,     9344 1451
    where F = CoH(meta) / CoH(ground).                            9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
    MT  16 (n,2n)                                                 9344 1451
    MT  17 (n,3n)                                                 9344 1451
    MT  18 fission                                                9344 1451
    MT  37 (n,4n)                                                 9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
    These sections below were replaced by the CoH excited state   9344 1451
    calculations.                                                 9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
    MT   1 total                                                  9344 1451
    MT   2 elastic = total - sum of partials                      9344 1451
    MT  51 - 56 discrete level inelastic scattering               9344 1451
    MT  91 continuum inelastic scattering                         9344 1451
    MT 102 radiative capture                                      9344 1451
                                                                  9344 1451
